[SHORT DESC]
Heals 25% HP when hit by an Electric-type attack. 
[LONG DESC]
<p>When this Pok√©mon is hit by an Electric-type attack, it gains 25% of its max HP. Thunder Wave is also absorbed. No secondary effects associated with the Electric-type attack will occur. A Ground-type Pokemon with Volt Absorb will not heal any HP. If Protect is successfully used against an Electric-type attack, Volt Absorb does not activate. If Substitute is used against an Electric-type attack, Volt Absorb does activate.</p>